{"tid":1519794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政權最畏懼嘅，係公民面對打壓，依然毫不畏懼","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:03:55.000Z","uid":89185,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee68ad2ad5c51e32ead929a70995095819f4cb0","tid":1519794,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"我地講好咗，八一八後，不分和勇。<br />\n我地唔係和理非，我地唔係勇武。<br />\n我地係香港人。<br />\n面對強權打壓，依然毫不畏懼嘅香港人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q1rkf_OSLiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq1rkf_OSLiY&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0maNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=909ff00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q1rkf_OSLiY</a><br />\n我會繼續記住由612到而家，有幾多人受傷，被捕，以死明志。<br />\n我會繼續記住政權有幾不義。<br />\n我會繼續記住煲底嘅約定。<br />\n人生而自由。每當我想起依一句話，就會有無窮嘅勇氣。<br />\n我希望大家都可以繼續勇敢面對。<br />\n最後一戰仍未到來，寒冬仍未過去。<br />\n我地香港人，繼續結伴同行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n八一八後，不分和勇。<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心。</span></span>"},{"pid":"da165e6e64326f8ce6657645db40c36e29edd556","tid":1519794,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n八一八後，不分和勇。<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心。</span></span>"},{"pid":"66e79a504638825ffcf9ac7937b705fc61c82d8d","tid":1519794,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n八一八後，不分和勇。<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心。</span></span>"},{"pid":"321ccf67e6a7d6898769c8f8fc79e0fc3084bcde","tid":1519794,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal